SIMPLE: listing
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Listing
<hw>List"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act or process of
one who lists (in any sense of the verb); <as>as, the <ex>listing</ex>
of a door; the <ex>listing</ex> of a stock at the Stock
Exchange.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The selvedge of cloth; list.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <fld>(Carp.)</fld> <def>The sapwood cut from the edge of
a board.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>4.</sn> <fld>(Agric.)</fld> <def>The throwing up of the soil into
ridges, -- a method adopted in the culture of beets and some garden
crops.</def> <mark>[Local, U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Listless</ent>⟦br⟧
